# Real-Time Risk Monitoring System - Instruction Map

This instruction map shows how to compose core_engine components into a comprehensive real-time risk monitoring and surveillance system for continuous portfolio oversight, limit monitoring, and automated risk response.

## Risk Monitoring Component Stack

### Real-Time Surveillance Brick Assembly
```
┌─────────────────────────────────────┐
│    HierarchicalSystemOrchestrator   │ ← System Control & Alert Coordination
├─────────────────────────────────────┤
│ RealTimeDataStreamer                │ ← Live Market & Portfolio Data
│ PositionMonitor                     │ ← Real-Time Position Tracking
│ PnLCalculator                       │ ← Live P&L Calculation
├─────────────────────────────────────┤
│ RiskLimitMonitor                    │ ← Continuous Limit Surveillance
│ VaRCalculator                       │ ← Real-Time VaR Calculation
│ StressTestEngine                    │ ← Continuous Stress Testing
│ CorrelationMonitor                  │ ← Dynamic Correlation Tracking
├─────────────────────────────────────┤
│ CentralRiskManager                  │ ← Risk Governance & Control
├─────────────────────────────────────┤
│ AlertEngine                         │ ← Multi-Level Alert System
│ AutomatedResponseSystem             │ ← Automated Risk Responses
│ RiskDashboard                       │ ← Real-Time Risk Visualization
│ ComplianceMonitor                   │ ← Regulatory Compliance Tracking
│ AuditTrail                          │ ← Complete Risk Audit Logging
└─────────────────────────────────────┘
```

